headline.main: Bulls Top Golden State in Warriors' 1st Game Without Durant
headline.print_headline: Bulls Top Golden State in Warriors' 1st Game Without Durant

lead_paragraph: Alex Burrows scored twice in his debut with the Ottawa Senators and led his new club to a 2-1 win over the Colorado Avalanche on Thursday night.
